WEBVTT

00:03.000 --> 00:04.210
那人不是我杀的  迈克尔
I didn't kill that man. Michael

00:04.220 --> 00:05.570
但是证据确凿
The evidence says you did.

00:05.580 --> 00:08.060
我是被陷害的
I was set up.

00:08.070 --> 00:10.200
把枪放下
Put down your weapon.

00:10.210 --> 00:13.110
我有义务判你入狱
I find it incumbent you see the inside of a prison cell.

00:13.120 --> 00:15.370
我想找个人  他叫林肯·布伦斯
I'm looking for someone,his name's Lincoln Burrows.

00:15.380 --> 00:16.930
杀死副总统哥哥的那个?
He killed the vice president's brother.

00:16.940 --> 00:18.640
你为什么这么急着要见布伦斯?
Why you wanna see Burrows?

00:18.650 --> 00:19.730
因为他是我哥哥
He's my brother.

00:19.740 --> 00:21.100
我要把你带出去
I'm getting you out.

00:21.110 --> 00:22.040
不可能
That's impossible.

00:22.050 --> 00:24.160
除非这个监狱是你设计的
Not if you designed the place.

00:24.170 --> 00:25.440
你看过蓝图了?
You've seen the blueprints.

00:25.450 --> 00:26.860
不止如此
Better than that.

00:26.870 --> 00:28.510
我把他们都纹在身上了
I've got 'em on me.

00:28.520 --> 00:30.120
你得找出是谁要至他于死地
You find out who's trying to bury him.

00:30.130 --> 00:31.590
没人要他死
Nobody is.

00:31.600 --> 00:32.870
证据确凿
The evidence was cooked.

00:32.880 --> 00:34.240
又来了个好管闲事的律师
A lawyer's poking around.

00:34.250 --> 00:36.570
任何威胁到咱们的人都要除掉
Anyone that's a threat is expendable.

00:36.580 --> 00:37.660
斯科菲尔德
Scofield

00:37.670 --> 00:40.080
给你找来个新朋友 海威尔 过来
Found you a new cellie.Haywire,get in here.

00:40.090 --> 00:41.700
有人找到了菲波纳奇
Someone found Fibonacci.

00:41.710 --> 00:42.880
是谁?
Who was this someone?

00:42.890 --> 00:44.680
菲波纳奇到底在哪儿?
Where is Fibonacci?

00:44.690 --> 00:47.000
我要告诉你  那才死定了
I give you that information,I'm a dead man.

01:10.010 --> 01:12.550
给我起来
On your feet.

01:12.780 --> 01:15.170
才几点啊?
What time is it?

01:15.180 --> 01:16.440
快起来
Get up.

01:16.450 --> 01:19.270
发生什么事了?
What's going on?

01:19.320 --> 01:21.190
贝利克
Bellick.

01:21.200 --> 01:22.170
贝利克
Bellick.

01:22.180 --> 01:25.300
贝利克 不要
 Bellick. No!

01:28.890 --> 01:30.900
贝利克 你要把我带哪儿去?
Bellick! Where are you taking...

01:30.910 --> 01:33.450
贝利克 贝利克 不要啊
Bellick,Bellick, No! Bellick!

01:33.460 --> 01:35.300
不 贝利克 不要
No! Bellick,no!

01:35.310 --> 01:37.150
贝利克  不 还有一个月呢
Bellick,no! I got a month.

01:37.160 --> 01:40.010
求你了 不要 贝利克
Please,no,Bellick!

01:40.020 --> 01:41.430
贝利克 不要
Bellick,no.

01:41.440 --> 01:42.710
贝利克  求你了
Bellick,please,no!

01:42.720 --> 01:45.280
不 不 还有一个月呢
No,I got a month

01:45.290 --> 01:47.610
求你了
Please!

01:47.620 --> 01:50.440
不 贝利克
No,Bellick...

02:21.780 --> 02:25.550
安息吧  林肯
Make your peace,Lincoln.

02:31.560 --> 02:34.670
开始吧
Let's get on with it.

03:20.200 --> 03:23.780
打开40号
Open 40.

03:31.410 --> 03:34.090
关闭40号
Close 40.

03:44.990 --> 03:48.530
海威尔  你想过逃出去么?
Haywire,you ever thought of breaking out?

03:48.540 --> 03:51.230
我出去后又能做什么呢?
What the hell would I do out there?

03:51.240 --> 03:53.030
只要不在这儿
Not be here.

03:53.040 --> 03:54.540
精神病院?
Halfway houses.

03:54.550 --> 03:58.010
看医生  吃药  定期接受检查?
Psych visits.Meds. Checking in with the PO.

03:58.020 --> 04:01.730
尿检  如此反复...
Urine tests. Keeping a job.

04:01.740 --> 04:03.610
我才不要呢
No.

04:03.620 --> 04:05.500
为什么这么问?
Why'd you ask?

04:05.510 --> 04:09.110
昨天有人在院子里问我这个 我不知道怎么回答
This guy was talking about it in the yard.I didn't know what to say.

04:09.120 --> 04:11.290
告诉贝利克长官
Tell Officer Bellick.

04:11.300 --> 04:16.090
他会帮你的  如果...
He'll make life easier for you if...

04:19.460 --> 04:21.660
如果什么?
If what?

04:21.670 --> 04:23.600
你的纹身
Your tattoos.

04:23.610 --> 04:26.530
纹身怎么了?
What about them?

04:26.810 --> 04:28.790
刻的是什么?
What are they of?

04:28.800 --> 04:30.570
看起来像是某个...
Like,some kind of...

04:30.580 --> 04:32.140
只是纹身罢了
They're just tattoos.

04:32.150 --> 04:35.360
该吃药了  海威尔
Candy time,Haywire.

04:39.290 --> 04:43.000
他们认为我患有严重的精神分裂症
They think I have schizo-affective disorder with bipolar tendencies.

04:43.010 --> 04:45.920
你觉得有吗?
Think you got it?

04:46.110 --> 04:49.080
无所谓了
Whatever.

04:54.510 --> 04:58.300
服下药丸  蠢医生就会走了
I take the pills to keep the quacks off my back.

05:02.650 --> 05:04.170
再见
Bye,now.

05:04.180 --> 05:06.860
闪开
Get out to the way.

05:14.300 --> 05:17.350
或许他们给你这东西是有原因的
You know,maybe they give you those things for a reason.

05:17.360 --> 05:18.660
没错
Yeah.

05:18.670 --> 05:20.650
为了把我变成白痴
To keep me dull.

05:20.660 --> 05:24.400
用一双无形的手铐锁住我
To keep me in their invisible freaking handcuffs.

05:24.410 --> 05:27.420
不过说真的  那纹身真不错
Seriously. Those tattoos,they're beautiful.

05:27.430 --> 05:30.610
介意我完整的看看么?
You mind if I,you know,look at the whole thing?

05:30.620 --> 05:33.600
事实上  我介意
I do,actually.

05:33.610 --> 05:34.910
为什么?
Why?

05:34.920 --> 05:37.140
你 站开
Yo. Stand clear.

05:37.150 --> 05:40.410
需要理由么?
Does there need to be a reason?

05:47.060 --> 05:48.830
苏克雷
Sucre.

05:48.840 --> 05:51.720
我不能和你说话  伙计
I'm not even talking to you,man.

06:30.150 --> 06:32.530
有什么不对头么?
What's the problem?

06:32.540 --> 06:34.180
没有我解决不了的
Nothing I can't handle.

06:34.190 --> 06:35.880
我知道有事
Well,I knew there was a problem.

06:35.890 --> 06:39.530
我在院子那头就看出事情有些不对了
I could tell by looking at you from across the yard.

06:39.540 --> 06:43.000
伙计们  我就说有事情不对吧?
Guys,didn't I say there was a problem?

06:43.010 --> 06:45.500
到底是怎么回事?
So what's the problem?

06:45.510 --> 06:48.340
你自己看
You're looking at it.

06:48.620 --> 06:49.790
什么? 海威尔?
What,Haywire?

06:49.800 --> 06:53.400
没错  我的新狱友
Yup. He's my new cell mate.

06:53.720 --> 06:54.840
这就有问题了
That's a problem.

06:54.850 --> 06:55.980
他从不睡觉
He doesn't sleep.

06:55.990 --> 06:57.390
那你都什么时候挖?
So when do you dig?

06:57.400 --> 06:59.330
我没法挖
I don't.

06:59.340 --> 07:02.680
嘿  咱俩现在可是在一条船上 
Hey,you and I are in bed now.

07:02.690 --> 07:03.820
你答应过我
You made me a promise.

07:03.830 --> 07:06.770
你说过咱们会逃出去的
You said that we were gonna get out of here.

07:06.780 --> 07:10.330
要是食言  我就宰了你
You renege now,and I'm gonna cut you.

07:10.340 --> 07:12.890
你好自为之吧
You better take care of your business.

07:12.900 --> 07:15.730
要不然我就给你好看
Or I will take care of you.

07:15.740 --> 07:18.910
祝你今天过得愉快
Have a nice day.

08:05.700 --> 08:08.610
真的能弄好么?
It's really coming together,isn't it?

08:08.620 --> 08:09.870
是的
Yup.

08:09.880 --> 08:11.530
能按时完工?
You think it'll be done in time?

08:11.540 --> 08:15.260
虽然我觉得里面要是 再有个凉亭会好一些
Well,I figure we still have the interior alcoves.

08:15.270 --> 08:17.530
而且柱子的工作量也不小
Pilasters to do,which is no small task.

08:17.540 --> 08:22.260
但是  我想按时完工没问题
But,yes. I think so.

08:22.270 --> 08:24.160
我不得不说  我...
Listen,I have to say I

08:24.170 --> 08:28.950
你为我所做的我真是感激不尽
I really appreciate all the effort that you put into this.

08:28.960 --> 08:34.140
真希望有什么能补偿你 比如付你工钱 或是...
I wish there was some way I could,you know,pay you,or something.

08:34.150 --> 08:37.890
有件事还真要请您帮忙
There is one thing you could do for me.

08:38.170 --> 08:39.940
我的狱友
My cell mate.

08:39.950 --> 08:42.550
啊 那个不用睡觉的疯子?
The inimitable Charles Patoshik.

08:42.560 --> 08:43.530
海威尔?
Haywire?

08:43.540 --> 08:45.230
原来你知道
Then you know.

08:45.240 --> 08:46.590
你就忍忍吧
Hold it right there.

08:46.600 --> 08:49.580
贝利克长官负全权责犯人的调度
Officer Bellick is in charge of cell transfers.

08:49.590 --> 08:51.630
你得找他商量商量
You're gonna have to talk to him about that.

08:51.640 --> 08:54.950
我试过  他好像认为我俩是天生的一对
I tried. But he seems to think we're a good match.

08:54.960 --> 08:56.090
他威胁到你了没有?
Has he threatened you?

08:56.100 --> 08:59.880
谁  海威尔还是贝利克?
Who? Haywire or Bellick?

08:59.890 --> 09:03.690
不幸的是  除非能证明有暴力
Unfortunately,unless there's some evidence of violence.

09:03.700 --> 09:06.970
或者性侵犯事件发生在你们之间
or sexual predation between cell mates.

09:06.980 --> 09:11.200
其余的请求一般是不予受理的
those kinds of requests fall on deaf ears around here.

09:11.210 --> 09:16.140
监狱里可没人有时间来管 什么性格不和之类的事情
Prison system's a little too crowded for requests based on personality.

09:16.150 --> 09:20.030
这里可不是什么度假胜地
It's not exactly Sandals out there.

09:22.320 --> 09:23.400
监狱长?
Warden?

09:23.410 --> 09:25.810
不好意思  您妻子来了
 Sorry. Your wife is here.

09:25.820 --> 09:27.200
什么?
What?

09:27.210 --> 09:30.550
不是应该4点到的么?
 She's not supposed to be here till four o'clock.

09:30.560 --> 09:33.800
贝蒂  无论如何也不能让她进来这里
Becky,do not let her come in here under any circumstances.

09:33.810 --> 09:36.220
不能在结婚纪念日之前让她看到这个
She's not supposed to see this until our anniversary.

09:36.230 --> 09:38.770
我这就出去
I'll be right out.

09:44.850 --> 09:46.490
嗨  亲爱的
Hi,sweetheart.

09:46.500 --> 09:47.900
来这么早
You're early.

09:47.910 --> 09:50.470
咱们去吃点东西
Let's go eat.

09:50.480 --> 09:52.340
你看起来怎么这么滑稽?
You're acting funny.

09:52.350 --> 09:53.100
有么?
I am?

09:53.110 --> 09:54.670
里面到底在干什么?
What's going on in there?

09:54.680 --> 09:57.700
只是在看一些文件
Just going over some files.

09:57.710 --> 10:00.440
贝蒂说你在开会
Becky said you were in a meeting.

10:00.450 --> 10:04.330
不会又是托莱多事件吧?
This isn't Toledo all over again,is it?

10:04.340 --> 10:05.940
托莱多?
Toledo?

10:05.950 --> 10:07.970
怎么可能?
How can you say that?

10:07.980 --> 10:09.640
那就不介意我进去看一下了
Then you won't mind if I look.

10:09.650 --> 10:12.090
朱蒂
Uh,Judy...

10:12.550 --> 10:15.450
监狱长  我没法再继续合作下去了
Warden,I'm not gonna be able to cooperate.

10:15.460 --> 10:18.320
再这样下去  我会被杀死的
I'd get killed if I did.

10:18.330 --> 10:21.680
约翰逊还在考虑
Johnson's still deciding.

10:21.690 --> 10:24.610
好 没你事了
Then you and I are done.

10:26.950 --> 10:29.120
你该早点告诉我
You should have just told me.

10:29.130 --> 10:32.500
每当你接触犯人的时候  你知道我有多紧张
Well,you know how anxious I get when you come around the inmates.

10:32.510 --> 10:35.310
贝蒂  叫警卫把约翰逊押回牢房
Becky,have a guard escort Johnson back to his cell.

10:35.320 --> 10:39.590
我稍后再处理 走吧  咱们吃饭去
I'll deal with him later.Come on,let's eat.

10:54.510 --> 10:55.880
你来这里干嘛?
What are you doing here?

10:55.890 --> 10:58.370
我是你的律师
I'm your attorney.

10:58.650 --> 11:02.340
代理你的案件
I'm representing you now.

11:02.950 --> 11:06.490
如果你不介意的话
If that's all right with you.

11:07.330 --> 11:09.980
上次我见到你时 还说我是个骗子
Last time I saw you,you called me a liar.

11:09.990 --> 11:12.200
世事难料
Things have changed.

11:12.210 --> 11:14.990
我现在相信你了
I believe you now.

11:26.960 --> 11:32.110
我和克拉博·西蒙斯 的前女友莱提莎谈过了
I got in touch with Crab Simmons' ex-girlfriend,Leticia.

11:32.120 --> 11:35.900
她证实了你的事情
She corroborated your story.

11:35.960 --> 11:37.690
她会作证么?
Will she testify?

11:37.700 --> 11:40.050
她失踪了
She's missing.

11:40.060 --> 11:42.700
我也说不好  我认为她被特情局盯上了
I don't know.I think the Secret Service got to her.

11:42.710 --> 11:43.930
特情局?
Secret Service?

11:43.940 --> 11:45.470
他们也牵扯进来了
They've been poking around.

11:45.480 --> 11:48.330
他们一出现  她就消失了 你怎么看?
They show up,she disappears.What do you think happenned?

11:48.340 --> 11:54.190
我没想到能牵扯到高层
I didn't realise it was that high up,you know?

11:54.690 --> 11:56.620
你知道我们面对的是什么人么?
Do you know what we're up against?

11:56.630 --> 12:00.770
我只知道凭借咱们中的 任何一个人都应付不了的
I know it's a lot more than either of us can handle on our own.

12:00.780 --> 12:02.890
司法公正处
Project Justice.

12:02.900 --> 12:04.390
好像听说过?
Why have I heard of them?

12:04.400 --> 12:06.190
命案都是他们处理
They handle death penalty cases.

12:06.200 --> 12:07.690
那里有个叫本·福斯克的
There's a guy,Ben Forsik.

12:07.700 --> 12:09.480
我把我所有掌握资料的拷贝都给他了
I sent him copies of everything I had.

12:09.490 --> 12:10.880
你到那说明一下情况
You could tell him what you found.

12:10.890 --> 12:13.780
或许他会帮助咱们
Maybe it'll be enough to bring him on board.

12:13.790 --> 12:16.330
好的
OK.

12:18.340 --> 12:22.490
塞巴斯蒂安怎么样了?
So,uh,how's Sebastian?

12:22.870 --> 12:25.170
你指什么?
What do you mean?

12:25.180 --> 12:30.690
你来这里找我  我是说 他不会介意吧?
Well,you being here.I mean,is he cool with it?

12:31.110 --> 12:35.180
我没告诉他
I haven't talked to him.

12:37.330 --> 12:39.970
婚约解除了
The engagement's off.

12:39.980 --> 12:43.960
真对不起
Sorry.

12:43.970 --> 12:47.410
你最好真是那么想的
You could at least say that like you mean it.

12:47.420 --> 12:49.580
真的
I do.

12:50.510 --> 12:55.300
你真是个差劲的说谎者
God,you always were a lousy liar.

12:55.910 --> 12:58.160
是的
Yeah.

12:59.770 --> 13:02.850
我还是去找司法公正处吧
I better get to Project Justice.

13:11.650 --> 13:12.420
维罗妮卡?
Veronica?

13:16.850 --> 13:19.090
多谢
Thank you.

13:19.100 --> 13:20.940
我剩下的时间不多了
 I didn't have a whole lot.

13:20.950 --> 13:24.780
等你出来后再谢我也不迟
You can thank me when I get you out of here.

13:40.980 --> 13:43.930
宝贝  是我  你在么?
Baby,it's me. Are you there?

13:43.940 --> 13:45.630
喂? 你在么?
Hello? Are you there?

13:45.640 --> 13:50.520
嘿  就算她在  她也显然不想理你
Hey. If she is,she obviously don't want to talk to you.

13:52.120 --> 13:53.660
今天是星期三  宝贝儿
It's Wednesday,babe.

13:53.670 --> 13:56.440
你会来看我的  对么?
You were gonna come around today,right?

13:56.450 --> 13:58.080
好吧  我得挂了
Look,I gotta hang up now.

13:58.090 --> 13:59.990
我得回去了
I gotta go back in the block.

14:00.000 --> 14:03.080
你会来的  对么?
but...you're gonna be here today,right?

14:03.090 --> 14:05.910
不要忘了我  亲爱的  我爱你
I'm your man,baby,and I love you.

14:05.920 --> 14:08.750
永远爱你
I do.

14:22.720 --> 14:25.610
像是某个地方
It's a pattern.

14:25.750 --> 14:27.020
你说什么?
What did you say?

14:27.030 --> 14:29.430
你的纹身...像是某个地方
Your tattoo. It's a pattern.

14:29.440 --> 14:32.410
你看错了
You're seeing things.

14:39.200 --> 14:41.800
让他和海威尔住在一起的是下策
Putting him in with Haywire is a low blow.

14:41.810 --> 14:45.330
什么? 他已经没事了
What? The shrinks cleared Haywire for re-entry into Gen Pop.

14:45.340 --> 14:48.080
而且他每天都会吃药  简直就像小猫一样乖
He's so doped up on meds he's like a kitten.

14:48.090 --> 14:50.030
一只杀死亲生父母的小猫
A kitten who murdered both his parents.

14:50.040 --> 14:51.390
出于尊敬  长官
With respect,sir.

14:51.400 --> 14:56.430
您要是再给斯科菲尔德特权的话 会影响到您的信誉的
If you give Scofield preferential treatment,it'll undermine your credibility.

14:56.440 --> 14:59.910
我知道您偏爱他  因为他很有头脑
I know you got a so spot for the guy because he's got brains.

14:59.920 --> 15:02.380
并且能帮您弄那个玩意儿
And he's helping you with that contraption.

15:02.390 --> 15:04.420
但他是个有暴力倾向的罪犯
But the guy's a violent criminal.

15:04.430 --> 15:07.080
正如其他的犯人一样 受到惩罚是罪有应得
He deserves punishment as much as the rest of these guys.

15:07.090 --> 15:08.600
你来这么久了也该知道
You've been here long you've to know that.

15:08.610 --> 15:11.600
我是感化重于惩罚
I'm less interested in punishment than I am in rehabilitation.

15:11.610 --> 15:15.460
