What stood out was that most death penalty cases

30:18.380 --> 30:20.850
往往有10年左右的上诉期
take ten years to exhaust all appeals.

30:20.860 --> 30:23.080
林肯却只有三年的时间
Lincoln got there in three.

30:23.090 --> 30:24.530
一切显得那么顺理成章
So for it to be expedited,

30:24.540 --> 30:27.250
定是出于某种政治的考虑  对么?
there had to have been some political influence,right?

30:27.260 --> 30:29.960
特伦斯·斯蒂德曼是副总统的哥哥对么?
Steadman was the vice-president's brother.

30:29.970 --> 30:31.400
这就不难相信了
It's not hard to believe.

30:31.410 --> 30:34.480
怎么可能? 他们搞定了所有的法官?
How? They got to every judge that rejected his appeal?

30:34.490 --> 30:37.420
根本用不着法官
It doesn't take ajudge.

30:37.690 --> 30:41.150
只要她的手下稍微做些手脚就行了
All it takes is a little special attention from one of his clerks.

30:41.160 --> 30:44.620
我对林肯被处死刑之快没有兴趣 我关心的是他们为什么要这么做
But how Lincoln got fast-tracked doesn't interest me. It's why.

30:44.630 --> 30:47.030
若他真是被陷害的 究竟又是为了什么呢?
If he was set up,then why?

30:47.040 --> 30:50.760
可能只有被害人才知道
I think the answer to that might lie in the victim.

30:50.770 --> 30:53.530
我们知道什么? 他是菲尔德公司的首席执行官对么?
What do we know? He was a CEO of EcoField,right?

30:53.540 --> 30:55.330
还是替代能源的倡导者
 He was pushing alternative energy.

30:55.340 --> 30:57.800
而且他做的很成功
Successfully pushing alternative energy.

30:57.810 --> 31:01.480
于是石油公司  沙特人  甚至是我们的政府...
Oil companies,the Saudis,even our government ...

31:01.490 --> 31:05.550
若斯蒂德曼消失的话 很多人都会从中受益
a lot of people stood to benefit with Steadman out of the picture.

31:06.300 --> 31:09.550
你为什么现在才受理这案子?
Why did you wait till now to take up this case?

31:09.560 --> 31:13.530
我也和别人一样  原以为是他干的
I thought he did it,like everybody else.

31:13.540 --> 31:15.760
希望还为时不晚
I just hope it's not too late.

31:15.770 --> 31:17.560
很可能已经晚了
It very well may be.

31:17.570 --> 31:20.770
你要有心理准备
You need to prepare yourself for that.

31:21.860 --> 31:24.220
那你呢?
What about you?

31:24.230 --> 31:28.020
为什么选择干这行?
Why death penalty work?

31:28.650 --> 31:32.070
我父亲含冤入狱15年
My father did 15 years for a crime he didn't commit.

31:32.080 --> 31:34.430
我深知一旦你被政府盯上了
I know that when the government gets you in their cross hairs,

31:34.440 --> 31:37.030
就很难再翻身了
you stand very little chance.

31:37.040 --> 31:39.260
这就是为什么
That's why.

31:42.150 --> 31:47.380
那么现在...需要我帮忙么?
Now,do you want my help?

32:09.030 --> 32:10.330
-我想加入  -太晚了
-I want in. -Too late.

32:10.340 --> 32:12.090
让我做什么都行  看见这双手了么?
I'll do anything.See this hand?

32:12.100 --> 32:13.270
简直就是挖掘机
These hands are digging machines.

32:13.280 --> 32:14.860
你想去中国? 我就挖到中国
And if you want to go to China ,I'll get you to China.

32:14.870 --> 32:17.210
我会像疯狂的穿山甲一样为你打地洞
I'll dig like a psychotic rodent if I have to.

32:17.220 --> 32:19.350
嫩鸡... 你一定要带上我
Fish,I gotta be back in.

32:19.360 --> 32:21.390
就目前来看  你没法回来
As of right now,there is no in.

32:21.400 --> 32:23.730
那边的凡高兄弟  是我的新狱友
Van Gogh over there is my new cell mate.

32:23.740 --> 32:25.010
你总会有办法的  对么?
But you're gonna do something about it ,right?

32:25.020 --> 32:27.380
-你会把他弄走的  -如果必要的话 我会的
-You're gonna get rid of him. -I'll do what's necessary.

32:27.390 --> 32:30.520
爱死你了
You're my boy.

32:31.980 --> 32:33.520
那你打算怎么办?
So how you gonna do it?

32:33.530 --> 32:35.590
只好这样了
Let's just put it this way.

32:35.600 --> 32:38.660
有人得受些皮肉之苦了
Someone's gonna get hurt.

32:45.720 --> 32:47.820
我们怎么没注意到这个?
How did we miss this guy?

32:47.830 --> 32:51.010
斯科菲尔德的父亲 在他出生时就已经不在了
Scofield's father was out of the picture by the time he was born.

32:51.020 --> 32:52.560
于是就跟了母亲的姓
Took his mother's name.

32:52.570 --> 32:56.870
斯科菲尔德没有前科 而且还是个全职的工程师
All right. Scofield had no priors and a full-time job as an engineer?

32:56.880 --> 32:57.640
没错
Correct.

32:57.650 --> 33:01.950
有一天他突然去抢银行  然后弃械投降
Then he goes and robs a bank,discharging a gun in the process,

33:01.960 --> 33:05.170
宣判的时候  他海申请被关在狐狸河监狱
so in sentencing he could manoeuvre his way to Fox River,

33:05.180 --> 33:08.580
同时他哥哥在那里的日子却不到一个月了
where his brother's scheduled to die in less than a month.

33:08.590 --> 33:10.310
显然他是有预谋的
Obviously,something's up.

33:10.320 --> 33:14.600
不过兄弟同在一所 监狱服刑倒也不稀奇
With all due respect,brothers are incarcerated together all over in the country.

33:14.610 --> 33:16.500
或许只是巧合
It may just be a coincidence.

33:16.510 --> 33:18.430
把弟弟弄走
Move on the younger brother.

33:18.440 --> 33:24.790
做干净点 以免坏了咱们的大事
Do it pre-emptively,before anything rises up,bites any of us in the ass.

33:36.990 --> 33:39.570
是路径图...
It's a pathway.

33:39.580 --> 33:42.100
它到底通向哪儿?
Where does it lead?

33:43.430 --> 33:46.160
你要把我带哪儿去?
Where are you taking me?

33:51.600 --> 33:54.360
你疯了么?
What? Are you nuts?

33:54.670 --> 33:55.920
长官
Officer!

33:55.930 --> 33:58.990
我要见长官
I need an officer!

33:59.000 --> 34:01.170
出什么事了?
What the hell's the problem down here?

34:01.180 --> 34:03.030
噢...这个婊子养的
What the... Son of a bitch.

34:03.040 --> 34:05.380
打开40号
Open up on 40.

34:05.390 --> 34:08.430
他身上有张路径图  通向某处
He's got the pathway on his body.It leads somewhere.

34:08.440 --> 34:09.760
退后  海威尔
Back off,Haywire

34:09.770 --> 34:12.710
不  看他的纹身  是张路径图
No,look.Look at his tattoos. It's a pathway.

34:12.720 --> 34:15.180
海威尔  我说了"退后" 你要来点胡椒水么?
Haywire.I said back off.You want a hot shot?

34:15.190 --> 34:16.790
我都说了  你看他的...
I'm telling you, look... Argh!

34:16.800 --> 34:19.270
退后  伙计 快进来帮忙
Back off, man.

34:19.280 --> 34:19.950
把他带走
Let's go. Get him out of here.

34:19.960 --> 34:21.920
那是通向地狱(之路)
It leads to hell!

34:21.930 --> 34:23.650
通向地狱
It leads to hell!

34:23.660 --> 34:26.050
通向地狱之路
It's a pathway to hell!

34:26.060 --> 34:30.260
他要把我们带到地狱
He's taking us all to hell!

34:47.000 --> 34:52.790
老伙计又团聚了 真是不错啊
So, the gang's all back together again.Well, ain't that swell?

34:52.800 --> 34:55.390
告诉过你不要背着我去找监狱长
I told you not to go around me with the Pope.

34:55.400 --> 34:59.030
可你就是不听  是不是?
But you just keep making waves, don't you?

35:07.790 --> 35:11.200
回来真好  欢迎归来
Good to be back, man. Good to have you back.

35:14.710 --> 35:19.080
咱们什么时候开始?
So, when do we get started?

35:45.590 --> 35:47.480
下午好 斯科菲尔德先生
Good afternoon, Mr Scofield.

35:47.490 --> 35:49.640
你好
Hello.

35:49.650 --> 35:51.710
今天感觉如何?
How are you feeling today?

35:51.720 --> 35:54.070
很好
Real good.

35:55.040 --> 35:57.400
又怎么了?
What happened?

35:57.410 --> 36:02.290
打篮球时吃了一暗肘
Caught an elbow playing basketball.

36:05.210 --> 36:06.790
我能看一下么?
Mind if I take a look?

36:06.800 --> 36:09.370
当然
By all means.

36:17.080 --> 36:19.300
你会把命丢了的  知道么?
You know you're gonna get killed in here, right?

36:19.310 --> 36:22.370
要是再不小心点的话
If you're not careful.

36:22.960 --> 36:25.240
我答应你
I'll make you a bet.

36:25.250 --> 36:28.980
要能活着出去
When I get out of here, alive,

36:28.990 --> 36:31.820
就请你共进晚餐
I'll take you to dinner.

36:32.880 --> 36:35.100
午餐或者咖啡什么的
Lunch. Cup of coffee.

36:35.110 --> 36:39.080
迈克尔  这种表达魅力的方式
Michael, this charm act

36:39.090 --> 36:43.740
正是你惹祸上身的原因
could be exactly what's getting you into trouble out in the yard.

36:47.770 --> 36:50.340
往前点
Lean forward.

37:00.880 --> 37:01.720
好的...
All right.

37:01.730 --> 37:02.950
你来到停车场
You went to the parking garage,

37:02.960 --> 37:05.460
特伦斯·斯蒂德曼就已经死了
Terence Steadman is already dead.

37:05.470 --> 37:06.550
没错
That's right.

37:06.560 --> 37:09.070
你发现后就跑掉了... 带着枪
You saw that, you ran? Took the gun?

37:09.080 --> 37:10.760
把枪扔了  扔哪儿了?
 Dumped the gun. Where?

37:10.770 --> 37:12.880
下水道  位于范布伦和威尔士
Storm drain. Van Buren and Wells.

37:12.890 --> 37:14.910
至今未被发现
Nobody ever found it.

37:14.920 --> 37:16.760
好的  那之后你做了什么?
What did you do after that?

37:16.770 --> 37:18.280
回到家?
Go back to your apartment?

37:18.290 --> 37:20.670
是的
Yeah.

37:22.360 --> 37:25.980
我吓坏了  想弄明白是怎么回事
I was freaking out,trying to figure out what had happened.

37:25.990 --> 37:30.070
然后发现浴缸里有条血迹斑斑的裤子
Then I saw the bloody pants in the tub.

37:32.310 --> 37:35.210
一分钟之后警察就赶到了
The cops, they busted in a minute after I got there.

37:35.220 --> 37:37.900
裤子上有斯蒂德曼的血迹
The pants, with Steadman's blood on them.

37:37.910 --> 37:41.380
第一个到现场的警察说亲眼 看到你在浴缸里洗那条裤子
First cop on the scene says he saw you washing them in the tub.

37:41.390 --> 37:42.150
他在说谎
He's lying.

37:42.160 --> 37:45.360
我手湿是因为洗脸弄的
My hands were wet after splashing water on my face.

37:45.370 --> 37:48.690
警察 把手举起来 把手举起来
Police! Let's see the hands! Hands up!

37:48.700 --> 37:51.320
我从未碰过那条裤子
I never touched those pants.

37:51.330 --> 37:53.080
再说说枪的事
Which brings us back to the gun,

37:53.090 --> 37:54.360
被你扔掉的那把枪
the one you dumped.

37:54.370 --> 37:55.110
这是设计好了的
It was planted.

37:55.120 --> 37:57.020
只能这么解释
Only way it could have got there.

37:57.030 --> 37:58.630
弹道完全吻合
Ballistics matched it to a slug...

37:58.640 --> 38:01.020
枪是嫁祸的 他们设计好了的
The gun was planted.

38:01.030 --> 38:02.560
就像血裤一样
Just like the pants.

38:02.570 --> 38:06.340
枪上有你的指纹
Your fingerprints were all over the gun.

38:08.730 --> 38:11.050
博...
Bo.

38:14.430 --> 38:15.530
博是谁?
Who's Bo?

38:15.540 --> 38:19.120
这一切都是他安排的
He's the guy who arranged everything.

38:20.030 --> 38:21.860
他让我前一天的晚上去找他
He had me come round the night before,

38:21.870 --> 38:24.370
试了几把枪  看哪把最适合
try a few guns, see which one felt right.

38:24.380 --> 38:25.980
那时就设计好了
That was the setup.

38:25.990 --> 38:27.860
凶器肯定就在那些枪之中
One of those must have been the murder weapon.

38:27.870 --> 38:30.310
枪上也就有了我的指纹
That's how they got my fingerprints on the gun.

38:30.320 --> 38:32.780
一定是这样
Had to be.

38:32.790 --> 38:34.780
那么这个叫 博的人...
All right. So this Bo,

38:34.790 --> 38:40.280
他逼你做这个  来偿还那9万元的欠款
he coerces you into doing this, all to clear a $90,000 debt?

38:40.500 --> 38:43.380
还扬言要杀了我儿子
He was gonna kill my son.

38:43.390 --> 38:44.240
进展如何?
Well?

38:44.250 --> 38:46.950
一大堆"不是我干的" 这些又起不了作用
Lot of "I didn't do it", don't count for much.

38:46.960 --> 38:49.380
监控录像  记录林肯扣动扳机的那盘...
The tape that shows Lincoln pulling the trigger.

38:49.390 --> 38:50.940
还在你手里么?  是的
 You got it?  Yeah.

38:50.950 --> 38:53.350
如果林肯说的属实  那盘录像就是伪造的
If Lincoln's telling the truth, the tape's lying

38:53.360 --> 38:57.480
咱们应该好好看看 看能不能发现什么
I think we should have a look,decide for ourselves.

39:03.550 --> 39:05.770
没人
You're clear.

39:21.760 --> 39:24.890
既然化学试剂能够腐蚀钢管
If the chemicals can eat through the iron pipes,

39:24.900 --> 39:27.520
为什么牙膏筒却没事?
how come they can't eat through the tube?

39:27.530 --> 39:31.100
只有当两种试剂混合才会发生发应
When the chemicals are combined,they become a corrosive.

39:31.110 --> 39:33.190
你是学化学的?
You studied chemistry or something?

39:33.200 --> 39:35.840
不是在学校学的
Not in school.

39:50.730 --> 39:53.560
你在医务室做什么了
But what you're doing up there in the infirmary,

39:53.570 --> 39:55.840
又和这里的事情有什么联系呢?
what's it gotta do with this here?

39:55.850 --> 39:58.930
打通这堵墙只是个开始
Getting through this wall is just the beginning.

39:58.940 --> 40:03.270
这里和外墙之间还有很多房间
There's a whole lot of real estate in between here and the outside walls.

40:03.280 --> 40:08.190
医务室是最靠近外墙的建筑
The infirmary's the closest building to those walls.

40:12.010 --> 40:15.100
...也是安全措施中最薄弱的环节
And the weakest link in the security chain.

40:15.110 --> 40:17.650
酷
Cool.

40:22.950 --> 40:26.430
我想挖的已经差不多了
I think I've removed enough grout to bust through.

40:26.440 --> 40:29.870
现在帮我弄点噪声
I'm gonna need you to make some noise.

40:38.430 --> 40:42.780
就这么点本事么?
Is that the best you can do?

40:42.850 --> 40:44.650
要相信我  哥们
Have some faith,papi.

40:44.660 --> 40:47.200
要相信我
Have some faith.

40:49.370 --> 40:51.650
闭嘴
Shut up!

41:35.800 --> 41:38.140
都给我闭嘴
Not one more word.

41:38.150 --> 41:43.330
谁再出声就关禁闭
Next inmate that opens his mouth goes in the hole.

41:55.820 --> 41:58.540
没事了
We're good.

42:25.360 --> 42:27.480
你还好吧?
You OK?

42:29.950 --> 42:32.340
工作的事
Work.

42:32.620 --> 42:34.900
没什么
It's fine.

42:37.160 --> 42:39.640
我来
I got it.

42:42.960 --> 42:44.100
还算顺利吧?
Everything all right?

42:44.110 --> 42:46.170
非常的顺利
Couldn't be better.

42:46.180 --> 42:48.900
进来坐会么? 我们正要吃晚餐呢
You want to come in?We just sat down to eat.

42:48.910 --> 42:53.410
不  我只想私下和你聊聊
No. I just wanted to stop by to tell you in person.

42:54.630 --> 42:56.650
问题解决了
Problem solved.

42:56.660 --> 42:58.090
这是什么?
What's this?

42:58.100 --> 43:00.340
移送申请
That is a transfer request.

43:00.350 --> 43:05.470
迈克尔·斯科菲尔德 明天就会被转走了
Michael Scofield is getting shipped out tomorrow.

43:09.280 --> 43:10.690
晚安
Have a good night.
